//!
//! ## Verification Model
//!
//! Commitments are verified by re-simulating the origin transaction at the **parent block**
//! state (i.e., `inclusion_block - 1`). This matches the builder's simulation context.
//!
//! The verifier checks:
//! 1. The origin transaction triggers the same async precompile
//! 2. The precompile input matches the commitment
//! 3. TTL and other constraints are valid

